<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA514_03_IH_0007_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="./../../common_practice/js/ema514_03_ih.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema514_03.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema514_03_ih_0007">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="7" class="is_star fraction_box_title" lang="y">
          <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>18</span>
                <span>30</span>
              </div>
              과 크기가 같은 분수를 만들려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.
            </div>
          </div>          
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <div class="flex justify_center">
          <div class="img">
            <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA514_03_IH/0007_img.png" alt="" />
            <span class="name" lang="y">채은</span>
            <span class="txt" lang="y">내가 만든<br />분수야.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 class="title" lang="y">채은이가 크기가 같은 분수를 만든 방법을 써 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box">
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field></math-field>
              <div class="example_box">
                <p lang="y">분모와 분자를 각각 0이 아닌 같은 수로 나누어 크기가 같은 분수를 만들었습니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <div lang="y">
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>18</span>
                      <span>30</span>
                    </div>
                    =
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>18÷2</span>
                      <span>30÷2</span>
                    </div>
                    =
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>9</span>
                      <span>15</span>
                    </div>
                    이므로 채은이는 분모와 분자를 각각 2로 나누어 크기가 같은 분수를 만들었습니다.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve">
                
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 class="title" lang="y">채은이와 같은 방법으로 크기가 같은 분수를 2개 더 만들어 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="flex justify_center">
            <div class="question_box bracket">
              <span class="bracket-l"></span>
              <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="(6)/(10)" text-align="center"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span class="comma">,</span>
              <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="(3)/(5)" text-align="center"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span class="bracket-r"></span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">분모와 분자를 각각 0이 아닌 같은 수로 나누어 크기가 같은 분수를 만듭니다.</p>
                  <div>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>18</span>
                      <span>30</span>
                    </div>
                    =
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>18÷3</span>
                      <span>30÷3</span>
                    </div>
                    =
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>6</span>
                      <span>10</span>
                    </div>
                    ,
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>18</span>
                      <span>30</span>
                    </div>
                    =
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>18÷6</span>
                      <span>30÷6</span>
                    </div>
                    =
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>3</span>
                      <span>5</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve">
                
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">전송</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
